  "detailed_description": "Realistic motorbike simulator.<br />\r\nReal wrist throttle and clutch!<br />\r\nDrive 49cc scooters to 1300cc big bikes!<br />\r\nTune and upgrade bikes.<br />\r\nAdd turbos and NOS to bikes.<br />\r\nEvery part changes bike driving attribute.<br />\r\n4 camera angles.<br />\r\nFree ride open world.<br />\r\nTimeattack.<br />\r\nChallenge mode.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEscape from cops and collect checkpoints on free ride.<br />\r\nControl wheelies using your wrist!<br />\r\nPop up wheelies using clutch  or motor power!<br />\r\nBrake+throttle to activate drifting mode!",
